\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Rename active takes and/or item notes from BWF/iXML and true source metadata using a fast ReaImGui UI.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Two templates: Take Name + Item Note (empty note template = skip).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Click tokens to insert at caret; caret snaps outside existing $tokens.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Robust around separators: safe with "--" and "__"; underscores no longer swallow preceding tokens.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Reads metadata once per selection ("Get Metadata") and caches it; configurable preview limit.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Apply uses current selection; reuses cache if unchanged; Undo / Redo supported.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Channel-aware tokens: $trk (auto per-take), $trkN, and $trkall (from iXML/BWF track list, with fallbacks).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab True source tokens: $srcfile, $srcbase, $srcext, $srcpath, $srcdir (actual media filename/paths).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Metadata panel + preview table with quick copy; export preview table as Tab or CSV.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Works on audio items; items without takes (empty/MIDI) can still update notes.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Requires: ReaImGui (install via ReaPack).\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Features:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Built with ReaImGUI for a compact, responsive UI.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Designed for fast, keyboard-light workflows.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 References:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab REAPER ReaScript API (Lua)\par}
